  "body": "### Description\nTo better maintain the pending pools of operations to include in proposed blocks:\n\n 1. When blocks are imported, only remove the operations they include from pools if the block is on our canonical chain\n 2. When a re-org occurs:\n    a. re-add operations from the old chain to the pending pools\n    b. remove operations from the new chain from pending pools\n\nOperations refer to items included in the block body - attestations, slashings and voluntary exits. ",
